content:
scoringscoring.best_score – score of the best proposalscoring.count_best – count of best address (with the lowest score)scoring.count_component – count of address components

outout.score - score of the best proposalout.explanation - explanation of the best proposalout.proposalCount - number of proposals to be rated (and possibly written out)out.foundProposalCount - number of proposals read during searching dictionaryout.possibleProposalCount - number of proposals seen during searching dictionaryout.possibleProposalsIndicator - indicates that the dictionary might contain more proposals to those seen

Aggregation functions are available in rating as well and the possible pseudo inputs there include (in addiction to those mentioned above)pafor proposal values,explfor explanation of these values 
			against the input andunexplfor unexplained (unmatched) input text.
